<item rdf:about="https://business.nikkei.com/atcl/seminar/19nv/120500136/030100692/">
<title>家業の売り上げを6倍に　きっかけは温泉湯豆腐の通販 (日経トップリーダー)</title>
<link>https://business.nikkei.com/atcl/seminar/19nv/120500136/030100692/</link>
